[/asy] The final Answer is  96
 ### Proof
 To start, we can draw in a line from where the altitude meets the base to one of the bottom corners as shown: [asy] size(150); draw((0,0)--(3,3)--(13,3)--(10,0)--cycle,linewidth(1)); draw((0,0)--(6.5,15)--(3,3),linewidth(1));
